metadata.name: Stuck in the Yucc - The Cactus House
metadata.description:
“Stuck in the Yucc” is the first piece in the Peculiar Homes collection by The Life of AIVAX, and was inspired by the family's time living in the desert. Photographs of the cactuses were taken around town and composed together in Photoshop. The spines of the cactus are all hand drawn. 

Artwork Size: 4000 x 5000
Created in Yucca Valley, CA
